{"title_page": "Gurukulam concepts", "text_new": "'''<nowiki/>'GURUKULAM CONCEPTS' is an innovative endeavor which includes Schools,Hostels,Coaching Centers for Competitive Exams, Tutorial Points for Academic Development and teachers training program component for Elementary, Secondary and Higher Secondary Education. The organisation is well known for its Social Works and Eco friendly noble ideas too. The Concepts begin in the year 2005 and was organized institutionally in the year 2012.'''\n\n'''<nowiki/>''' \n[[File:Gurukulamlogo.jpg|alt=Gurukulam Concepts|thumb|The Logo]]\nThe institution 'Gurukulam'  at Borgang under Biswanath District of Assam,India was established in February 2019. It is a complete residential study arena which offers a convenient and healthy study environment to the students of various educational institutions at Borgang. Moreover,the branches of the institution focus on imparting learning capabilities among students and teaching skills among teachers too.   \n\nThe Hostel cum Coaching Institute at Borgang offers various facilities to the students with proper career guidance for a balanced cognitive, social, interpersonal, psychological and moral development too. The 'Gurukulam' has been set up at Marangoan, Borgang of Biswanath District of Assam having a clear vision to achieve the overall development of a child as in the ancient Indian education system of The Gurukulas.  \n\n\n\nHowever, the institution also gives a lot of attention for the teachers' training programme to make teaching-learning interesting and joyous. The ICT based teachers training programme is one of the vital task of the institution.\n\n\n\nIt also gives immense pleasure to inform you that we are running our Tutorial Points at Batiamari and Biswanath Chariali for a proper understanding of the prevailing education scenario at various schools of the locality too. Carrier guidance programme and Coaching for CTET, ATET, JNVST(VI), JNVST(IX)  and other competitive exams are carried out from time to time.\n\n<br />\n\n=== '''These are some of the branches and functions of Gurukulam prevailing in recent times :''' ===\n\n* <u>'''''Gurukulam, Borgang. Biswanath. Assam :'''''</u> \n\n<blockquote>\n# --Hostel                            \n# --Carrier Counselling and Coaching Hub.\n# --Tutorial Point.                           \n# --Teachers' Training Arena.</blockquote>\n\n*<u>'''''Gurukulam, Batiamari. B'''''</u><u>'''''iswanath. Assam :'''''</u>\n\n<blockquote>\n# --Tutorial Point.              \n# --Carrier Counselling and Coaching Hub.</blockquote>\n\n*<u>'''''Gurukulam, Biswanath Chariali. Bi'''''</u><u>'''''s'''''</u><u>'''''w'''''</u><u>'''''an'''''</u><u>'''''a'''''</u><u>'''''th. Assam'''''</u>\n\n<blockquote>\n# --Tutorial Point.                  \n# --Teachers' Training Arena.</blockquote>\n\n*<u>'''''Projected soon at Guwahati, Jakhalabanda and Goruduba too.'''''</u>\n\n'''''<code>May visit Gurukulam's blog-  [https://mygurukulam.blogspot.com/ https://mygurukulam.blogspot.com]</code>'''''\n", "text_old": "'''<nowiki/>'GURUKULAM CONCEPTS' is an innovated endeavor which includes Schools,Hostels,Coaching Centers for Competitive Exams, Tutorial Points for Academic Development and teachers training program component for Elementary, Secondary and Higher Secondary Education. The organisation is well known for its Social Works and Eco friendly noble ideas too. The Concepts begin in the year 2005 and was organized institutionally in the year 2012.'''\n\n'''<nowiki/>''' \n[[File:Gurukulamlogo.jpg|alt=Gurukulam Concepts|thumb|The Logo]]\nThe institution 'Gurukulam'  at Borgang under Biswanath District of Assam,India was established in February 2019. It is a complete residential study arena which offers a convenient and healthy study environment to the students of various educational institutions at Borgang. Moreover,the branches of the institution focus on imparting learning capabilities among students and teaching skills among teachers too.   \n\nThe Hostel cum Coaching Institute at Borgang offers various facilities to the students with proper career guidance for a balanced cognitive, social, interpersonal, psychological and moral development too. The 'Gurukulam' has been set up at Marangoan, Borgang of Biswanath District of Assam having a clear vision to achieve the overall development of a child as in the ancient Indian education system of The Gurukulas.  \n\n\n\nHowever, the institution also gives a lot of attention for the teachers' training programme to make teaching-learning interesting and joyous. The ICT based teachers training programme is one of the vital task of the institution.\n\n\n\nIt also gives immense pleasure to inform you that we are running our Tutorial Points at Batiamari and Biswanath Chariali for a proper understanding of the prevailing education scenario at various schools of the locality too. Carrier guidance programme and Coaching for CTET, ATET, JNVST(VI), JNVST(IX)  and other competitive exams are carried out from time to time.\n\n<br />\n\n=== '''These are some of the branches and functions of Gurukulam prevailing in recent times :''' ===\n\n* <u>'''''Gurukulam, Borgang. Biswanath. Assam :'''''</u> \n\n<blockquote>\n# --Hostel                            \n# --Carrier Counselling and Coaching Hub.\n# --Tutorial Point.                           \n# --Teachers' Training Arena.</blockquote>\n\n*<u>'''''Gurukulam, Batiamari. B'''''</u><u>'''''iswanath. Assam :'''''</u>\n\n<blockquote>\n# --Tutorial Point.              \n# --Carrier Counselling and Coaching Hub.</blockquote>\n\n*<u>'''''Gurukulam, Biswanath Chariali. Bi'''''</u><u>'''''s'''''</u><u>'''''w'''''</u><u>'''''an'''''</u><u>'''''a'''''</u><u>'''''th. Assam'''''</u>\n\n<blockquote>\n# --Tutorial Point.                  \n# --Teachers' Training Arena.</blockquote>\n\n*<u>'''''Projected soon at Guwahati, Jakhalabanda and Goruduba too.'''''</u>\n\n'''''<code>May visit Gurukulam's blog-  [https://mygurukulam.blogspot.com/ 